CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Addentax Group Corp is an investment holding company. The company's operating segment includes Garment manufacturing; Logistics services; Epidemic prevention supplies; Property management and subleasing and Corporate and other. It generates maximum revenue from the Logistics services segment. The Logistics services segment provides logistic services. Geographically, it derives a majority of its revenue from China.
